lead_paragraph: When Dwyane Wade was a free agent in 2010, he got a Chicago Bulls jersey when he met with his hometown team. He took it home, put it on and took a picture. Then he deleted it.

headline.print_headline: Wade Excited to Join Hometown Bulls
